                   GO  TO  2001-INPUT-CHK-EXT
               END-IF
           END-IF
      *
      *    患者ＩＤに変換             
           IF      ONLINEQUAREQ1-PATIENT-ID
                                   =   SPACE
               MOVE    ZERO            TO  WRK-PTID
               MOVE    SPACE           TO  WRK-PATIENT-ID
           ELSE
               INITIALIZE                  ORCSPTNUMAREA
               MOVE    ONLINEQUAREQ1-PATIENT-ID
