           MOVE    SPA-HOSPNUM     TO  ONSKAKU-HOSPNUM
      *****MOVE    WRK-PTID        TO  ONSKAKU-PTID
           MOVE    ONLINEQUAREQ1-UUID
                                   TO  ONSKAKU-TBL-UUID
